{"categories":["travel-leisure","events"],"collections":"","description":"Experience the allure of sophistication with our dynamic one-column email layout, perfect for promoting your travel and events. The template is beautifully crafted in a light and refreshing green hue, combined with a clean white backdrop, exuding an aura of elegance. With a sans serif typography for a modern and minimalist appeal, the layout is designed to captivate your audience's attention. One of the unique features of this template is the dynamic countdown, a powerful tool to build anticipation and excitement for your upcoming events or travel destinations. The light design elements make your content shine, ensuring your message is delivered with impact and style. Elevate your email marketing with this sleek, modern template.","short_description":"Discover sophistication with our one-column email layout, ideal for promoting travel and events. Featuring a light green hue on a white backdrop, sans serif typography, and a dynamic countdown, this template captivates audiences and builds anticipation for upcoming events. Elevate your marketing with our sleek, modern design.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/Beefree_TemplateCatalog_ProfileImage_400x400_1.png","description":"A team of passionate designers, marketers, and technologists with an understanding that great design inspires action. At Beefree, we’re committed to creating responsive, mobile-friendly, and high-converting templates that empower teams to get more done with less time.","short_description":"","display_name":"Beefree Team","id":"beefree-team"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\"><head><title></title><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"><!--[if mso]><xml><o:OfficeDocumentSettings><o: